text: Ærest an norðan fram ceddanleage to langanleage bromleaginga mearc & leofsuhæma.
Þanne fram langanleage to ðam wonstocce.
Þanne fram ðam wonstocce be modinga hæma mearce to cinta stigole.
Þanne fram cintan stigole be modinga hæma mearce to earnes beame.
Ðanne fram earnes beame cræg sætena haga on easthealfe sced hit to leowsandene ðanne fram leowsandene to swelgende.
Ðanne fram swelgende crægsetenahaga to siox slihtre.
Ðanne fram seox slihtre to fearnbeorhginga mearce.
Fearn beorginga mearc hit sced to cystaningamearce.
Cystaninga mearc hit sced suðan to weardsetle.
Ðanne fram weardsetle cystaningamearc to wichæma mearce.
Ðanne seo west mearc be wichæma mearce ut to bipple styde.
Þonne fram bipple styde to acu styde to beoh hæma mearce.
Ðonne belimpað þær to ðam lande.
An on ut wealda brocces ham ðæs dennes nama.
And þæs oðres dennes nama sænget hryc.
Billan ora is þæs þriddan nama.
Þonne twa denn an glæppan felda.
